    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-f669e527-3b95-4664-85ba-4b1865c3318f">
                Mr. Swingler
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f669e527-3b95-4664-85ba-4b1865c3318f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-12-07/debates/22ecdd4a-334b-489d-aa20-a65df3838b86/GermanArmamentsAndTroops(SecondWorldWar)#contribution-f669e527-3b95-4664-85ba-4b1865c3318f">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister if he will publish in HANSARD the text of the order he sent to Field Marshal Montgomery in 1945 concerning <span id="772" class="column-number" data-column-number="772"></span> the need for careful stacking of captured German arms in case it should be necessary to return them to German troops for fighting against the Russians.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f669e527-3b95-4664-85ba-4b1865c3318f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-12-07/debates/22ecdd4a-334b-489d-aa20-a65df3838b86/GermanArmamentsAndTroops(SecondWorldWar)#contribution-f669e527-3b95-4664-85ba-4b1865c3318f">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>







<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-30d753b1-e1e1-40bf-b8a4-1e5068ad425a'>
            
<p class="">46.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-4635a102-a603-4a07-9775-f14afdf7ed42">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
