        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-4635a102-a603-4a07-9775-f14afdf7ed42">
                Mr. Dodds
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-4635a102-a603-4a07-9775-f14afdf7ed42" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-12-07/debates/22ecdd4a-334b-489d-aa20-a65df3838b86/GermanArmamentsAndTroops(SecondWorldWar)#contribution-4635a102-a603-4a07-9775-f14afdf7ed42">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister what were the instructions contained in his telegram to General Montgomery, in May, 1945, concerning captured German arms.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-4635a102-a603-4a07-9775-f14afdf7ed42" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-12-07/debates/22ecdd4a-334b-489d-aa20-a65df3838b86/GermanArmamentsAndTroops(SecondWorldWar)#contribution-4635a102-a603-4a07-9775-f14afdf7ed42">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>







<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-23d1b65b-bdff-433e-9ba0-526eb206c253'>
            
<p class="">50 and 51.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-f395dd4d-2a3e-448b-bb42-23eab35ac1d5">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-f395dd4d-2a3e-448b-bb42-23eab35ac1d5">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-f395dd4d-2a3e-448b-bb42-23eab35ac1d5">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-f395dd4d-2a3e-448b-bb42-23eab35ac1d5">
                Mr. Warbey
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f395dd4d-2a3e-448b-bb42-23eab35ac1d5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-12-07/debates/22ecdd4a-334b-489d-aa20-a65df3838b86/GermanArmamentsAndTroops(SecondWorldWar)#contribution-f395dd4d-2a3e-448b-bb42-23eab35ac1d5">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister (1) whether he will now publish in the OFFICIAL REPORT Or in a White Paper the text of the messages sent in 1945 to Field Marshal Montgomery concerning the preparations to be made for the use of German troops to resist the advance of Soviet forces beyond a certain point;<p></p> (2) whether he is now in a position to state the terms of the arrangements made in May, 1945 between Field Marshal Montgomery and Field Marshal von Busch, acting on behalf of Grand-Admiral DÃ¶nitz, for the maintenance in being of German armed forces and for the collection and stacking of their arms.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f395dd4d-2a3e-448b-bb42-23eab35ac1d5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-12-07/debates/22ecdd4a-334b-489d-aa20-a65df3838b86/GermanArmamentsAndTroops(SecondWorldWar)#contribution-f395dd4d-2a3e-448b-bb42-23eab35ac1d5">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-b53623e7-594d-499c-af88-69ba54dedc8b">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-b53623e7-594d-499c-af88-69ba54dedc8b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-b53623e7-594d-499c-af88-69ba54dedc8b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b53623e7-594d-499c-af88-69ba54dedc8b">
                The Prime Minister (Sir Winston Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b53623e7-594d-499c-af88-69ba54dedc8b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-12-07/debates/22ecdd4a-334b-489d-aa20-a65df3838b86/GermanArmamentsAndTroops(SecondWorldWar)#contribution-b53623e7-594d-499c-af88-69ba54dedc8b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">It has not been found possible to find the text of any message sent by me to Field Marshal Montgomery in May, 1945, concerning captured German arms. Every effort has been made and will continue to be made to find it. I will, of course, publish in the OFFICIAL REPORT any result should it be achieved. I certainly proposed around this time that the destruction of captured German arms should be delayed and my telegrams have been published. With regard to Question No. 51, in the name of the hon. Member for Broxtowe (Mr. Warbey), Field Marshal Montgomery has also reported to me that no arrangements of this kind were ever discussed between him and Field Marshal von Busch and no German armed forces were maintained in being after their unconditional surrender.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b53623e7-594d-499c-af88-69ba54dedc8b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-12-07/debates/22ecdd4a-334b-489d-aa20-a65df3838b86/GermanArmamentsAndTroops(SecondWorldWar)#contribution-b53623e7-594d-499c-af88-69ba54dedc8b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





